# Tailwind CSS Guidelines

## Design System
- Use consistent spacing: space-2, space-4, space-6, space-8
- Stick to color palette: primary-500, gray-600, etc.
- Follow typography scale: text-sm, text-base, text-lg, text-xl
## Mobile-First Classes
- Start with mobile styles, add responsive variants
- Use flex and grid for layouts
- Implement proper form styling with focus states

## Component Patterns
- Card: "bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm"
- Button: "bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg"
- Input: "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500"
